videos.description: Khalil Iverson cuts to the hoop and throws down a vicious one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Iverson brings the hammer with ferocious dunk

videos.description: Ethen Happ's turnover leads to a massive Justin Smith alley-oop.
videos.headline: Happ turnover leads to huge Smith alley-oop

videos.description: Rob Phinisee puts in an acrobatic layup to help push the game into overtime.
videos.headline: Phinisee's tough layup helps push game to OT

videos.description: D'Mitrik Trice squares up and buries a three to tie the game late in overtime.
videos.headline: Trice buries clutch 3 to tie it late in OT

videos.description: De'Ron Davis grabs the pass and puts in an and-1 layup putting Indiana up 3 in double OT.
videos.headline: Davis breaks the press and scores tough and-1 late in 2OT
